extends layout
block content

    h2 #{peakList.length} / 35 high peaks sumitted so far.
    p Here's a list of the Catskills 3500 high peaks that I've hiked so far. I'm working on hiking all of them to join the <a href="http://catskill-3500-club.org/" target="_blank">Catskills 3500 Club</a>. 

    table.table.table-striped
        tr
            th Name 
            th Height
            th Hiked
        each peak in peakList 
            tr
                td #{peak.name}
    